# Creative Coding Skill

## Skill Description

This skill enables agents to build award-winning, production-grade creative web experiences using GSAP, TailwindCSS, and React-based frameworks. Use it when building portfolio sites, marketing pages, interactive showcases, or any project requiring premium motion design and visual polish.

**Activate when the user asks for:**
- Animated landing pages or portfolio sites
- Scroll-driven storytelling or interactive sections
- Premium motion effects (parallax, reveals, transitions, loaders)
- Any site targeting Awwwards, FWA, or similar creative benchmarks
- Luxury, editorial, or high-craft brand experiences

