## Animation Timing Reference

### Entrance Animations

| Type | Duration | Easing | Stagger |
|------|----------|--------|---------|
| Fade in | 0.6s | power2.out | — |
| Slide up | 0.8s | power4.out | — |
| Char reveal | 1.0s | power4.out | 0.02s |
| Word reveal | 0.8s | power3.out | 0.08s |
| Line reveal | 1.0s | power4.out | 0.12s |
| Clip reveal | 1.2s | power4.out | — |
| Luxury settle | 1.4s | power3.out | — |

### Scroll Animations

| Type | Scrub | Feel |
|------|-------|------|
| Parallax drift | true (0.5–1s) | Weightless |
| Media expand | 1 | Substantial |
| Pin progress | true | Locked |
| World reveal | false (timeline) | Cinematic |

### Easing Quick Reference

- `power4.out` — Dramatic deceleration, hero entrances
- `power2.inOut` — Balanced, transitions
- `power3.out` — Smooth, general reveals
- `elastic.out(1, 0.4)` — Springy, magnetic reset
- `expo.out` — Snappy, UI feedback
- `none` — Scrub animations, linear progress

